include ../header
    tr
        td
            table(border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0', style='border-collapse: separate; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; width: 100%; padding: 0 20px;')
                tr
                    td(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: top;')
                        h3(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; Margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 20px; color: #5A443D;') Hi #{first_name},
                        p(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; Margin-top: 0; Margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5A443D; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5em;')
                            | We noticed that you requested to resend your One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your account. Please use the OTP below to complete your verification process:
                        h3(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; Margin-bottom: 8px; margin-top: 20px; color: #5A443D;')

                        h3(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; Margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 20px; color: #5A443D;') Your OTP: #{otp}
                        p(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; Margin-top: 0; Margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5A443D; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5em;') 
                            | (Note: This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes.)
                        p(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; Margin-top: 0; Margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5A443D; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5em;')
                            | If you did not request this, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately.

                        p(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; Margin-top: 0; Margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5A443D; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5em;') 
                            | Thank you,
                        p(style='font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px; Margin-top: 0; Margin-bottom: 20px; color: #5A443D; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.5em;') 
                            | Team #{appName}
        include ../footer